Paul Wesley https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Paul_Wesley 0 Paweł Tomasz Wasilewski (Polish: ['pavɛl vaɕi'lɛfskʲi]; born July 23, 1982), known professionally as Paul Wesley and formerly as Paul Wasilewski, is an American actor, director, and producer. He is best known for his roles as Aaron Corbett in the miniseries Fallen, Stefan Salvatore on the supernatural drama series The Vampire Diaries, and as Eddie Longo on the anthology series Tell Me a Story.
